<L>__{exterior meadow day}
<A>__{med. shot. graham drives the horses through the creek and into the meadow. through the trees the forster camp can be seen. graham glances over, then suddenly pulls on the reins. as the horses stop, he twists the reins around the whip stock, grabs his rifle from under the seat, leaps out and hurries forward toward the camp.}
